<div class="content" name="Security_ORPC_Extension" uuid="460384e9-fdbe-4fc1-b3d5-ca70176840d9"><p>The Security ORPC Extension structure is used to specify the
version, style, and number of security property collections in the out-of-band
data sent by the security ORPC extension.</p><table>
